%p{ style: 'margin-bottom: 36px' } Hello #{@user.name},

%p
  %u Upcoming Events

%p{ style: 'margin-bottom: 36px' }
  %a{ href: calendar_url }= calendar_url

%p
  %u New Members This Month

%ul{ style: 'padding-left: 18px' }
  - @new_users.each do |u|
    %li
      - if u.url.blank?
        %span>= u.name
      - else
        %a{ href: u.url }>= u.name
      - unless u.showcase_text.blank?
        = ", #{u.showcase_text}"

%p{ style: 'margin-bottom: 36px' }
  %a{ href: graphs_full_url } See all members

%p
  %u Billing Invoice

%p
  For each other member you connect to on Twitter or Facebook, your membership is discounted by Â£1 / yr.
  %br/
  You've made #{@num_new_connections} new connections this month, and there are still #{@num_users - @num_connections} members you haven't connected to yet.
  %br/
  To make sure this is up to date,
  %a{href: check_friends_connections_url} refresh your social accounts.

%table{ style: 'border-collapse: collapse' }
  %tbody
    %tr
      %td{ style: 'padding-right: 18px' } Membership Tier:
      %td{ style: 'padding-right: 18px' }= @subscription.plan.name
      %td{ style: 'padding-right: 18px' }= positivize_zero_val(@subscription.plan.value)
    %tr
      %td{ style: 'padding-right: 18px' } Maven Discount:
      %td{ style: 'padding-right: 18px' }= pluralize(@num_connections, 'connection')
      %td{ style: 'padding-right: 18px' }= positivize_zero_val(@user.discount / -12)
  %tfoot
    %tr
      %td{ style: 'padding-right: 18px; border-top: 1px solid #000'} Total:
      %td{ style: 'padding-right: 18px; border-top: 1px solid #000'}
      %td{ style: 'padding-right: 18px; border-top: 1px solid #000'}= positivize_zero_val(@discounted_total)

%p{ style: 'margin-bottom: 36px' }
  You will be billed with your card ending in #{@card_num} (
  %a{href: edit_subscription_url }> change payment details
  )

%p{ style: 'color: #555'}
  Any problems with your membership, or if you see anything funny with this email, please contact
  %a{ href: 'mailto:ed@nwspk.com' } ed@nwspk.com

%p
  %strong Newspeak House
